{"tid":988300,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"FIFA19 Ultimate Team 討論區（187）𡃁仔卡能屌打icon卡嗎","createTime":"2019-01-20T02:57:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-20T06:03:29.000Z","uid":121450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b8a15b7c89113e67337ac04d647829a1cd243825","tid":988300,"uid":121450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T02:57:46.000Z","msg":"歡迎大家加入FIFA19 Ultimate Team討論區<br />\n<br />\n開始前請先睇Q&amp;A，睇完搵唔到你想知既野先問，好多你想知既野都係第一版！拜託曬！ <br />\n<br />\nFIFA UT web app: <a href=\"https://www.easports.com/fifa/ultimate-team/web-app\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.easports.com%2Ffifa%2Fultimate-team%2Fweb-app&d=CH2%2BOu%2FXd5cykt%2BSaDfKp0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=8c8cdaca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.easports.com/fifa/ultimate-team/web-app</a><br />\n<br />\n球員資料database: <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://futhead.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffuthead.com&d=CH2%2BOu%2FXd5cykt%2BSaDfKp0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=694f2d51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://futhead.com</a> ;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://futwiz.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffutwiz.com&d=CH2%2BOu%2FXd5cykt%2BSaDfKp0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=c08f1913\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://futwiz.com</a> ;<br />\n<br />\nSBC 答案 (參考idea, 抄足貴到仆街)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.futbin.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.futbin.com&d=CH2%2BOu%2FXd5cykt%2BSaDfKp0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=a7aa8329\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.futbin.com</a><br />\n<br />\nFUT DATABASE <br />\n<a href=\"http://easports.com/fifa/ultimate-team/fut/database\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Feasports.com%2Ffifa%2Fultimate-team%2Ffut%2Fdatabase&d=CH2%2BOu%2FXd5cykt%2BSaDfKp0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=142d22e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://easports.com/fifa/ultimate-team/fut/database</a><br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A <br />\n1.係咪有金包送架? <br />\n答:係 game入面有張卡，其中一條係金包code<br />\n如果有, 係PS Store入面入code, 每星期就可以拎一包金包，記住唔係一次過拎晒<br />\n<br />\n2. 點賺錢? <br />\n答:踏實d, 打杯打比賽, 要快手就去淘寶課金, 切記今年EA&rdquo; 話&rdquo; 會嚴打買賣coins, 後果自負 <br />\n玩耐左可以試下炒卡。 <br />\n另外要留意賣卡會收「稅」，成功交易會抽5%，如賣10,000 coins成交，實收9,500 <br />\n<br />\n3. 咩係chemistry? <br />\n答:簡單d黎講, 高chemistry d隊員走位好d唔會成碌木咁唔走位, 另外個人chemistry會影響能力 <br />\n<br />\n4. 咁點加chemistry呀? <br />\n答:位置、球員之間既連線、教練、loyalty等等都會影響chemistry。 <br />\n<br />\n5. 咩係綠色連線? <br />\n答:球員同球員之間ge連線 <br />\n有3個原素 <br />\na.國籍 b.聯賽 c.球隊 <br />\n符合兩樣就夠, 咁樣有綠色連線 <br />\n一樣的話都有橙色 <br />\n<br />\n6. 咩係IF?咩係TOTW?點解有d卡會係黑色?<br />\n答:每星期三晚2點am都會有新既TOTW (team of the week) <br />\n出既人會有張加強版既黑色卡，又叫IF (in form) <br />\nNIF (not in form)係指有出過IF既人既普通版<br />\n黑卡因為多數只會出一個星期唔會再出，所以相當保值 <br />\n<br />\n7. 點解有時會有d限數量既pack? <br />\n答:EA有時會出promo pack，如15,000 coins既premium jumbo pack ，同有special promo pack之類，呢個係唔定時，視乎係咩種類既pack，可以抽5次或者10次，最貴既100K pack (24個全閃金球員)就只限抽一次 <br />\n要留意EASPORTSFIFA既twitter <br />\n<br />\n8.chemistry style係咩黎?持續幾耐? <br />\n答: 唔同chemistry style會對球員某d 能力有唔同提升, 每個球員一開始都有basic呢個style <br />\n你會見到每項能力都有一格V形箭嘴(假設chemistry 10), 唔代表果項能力 1 <br />\nchemistry style卡係永遠套用於某個球員, 直至你apply另一張落去 <br />\n<br />\n9: 隻Game 有無 handicap? 咩係handicap<br />\n答: 有handicap已經係公開o既秘密,而Handicap會令你經常有著數, 例如55波爭贏, 射門入球率大增 <br />\n而點先會令佢出現, 通常d人會透過壓星(壓Rating) 去令佢出現 <br />\n<br />\n10: 你地成日講H/H, H/M, M/L 係乜勁呀? <br />\n答: 代表球員work rate, 分H-high, M-medium, L-low<br />\nH/H就則係個球員atk同def work rate都係high<br />\n<br />\n11: 乜野係ONE TO WATCH呢？<br />\n答: 就係呢個球員（球員A）今季先轉會，咁就有幸比FIFA觀察<br />\n屌 你見到果啲黑卡 果啲叫inform卡，if卡數值定死左，就算佢之後再有好表現，都係會再出一張新卡。你成張藍色果啲叫otw卡 係會跟inform卡 upgrade數值，咁你就唔洗次次都要買新卡囉，另外OTW卡都會跟埋IF卡面<br />\n<br />\n12: SBC 點解跟網上嘅陣會唔夠CHEM? [FROM FIFA搏擊會]<br />\n答: 其實大家可以睇睇你班球員有無loyalty，因為抽返嚟嘅球員同踢過十場嘅球員都會有一點為上限嘅loyalty<br />\n刷loyalty方法：<br />\n開波，踢郁左個波之後，出去PS嘅設定，網絡入面測試網絡，如是者十場，又立即得，得咗！咁呢個方法就唔會計敗場，但會用多左時間！<br />\n<br />\n13:抽到xxxxxx應該賣定自用?<br />\n答: 我打機定你打機呀? 同三姑六婆問啲股票揸定沽有咩分別<br />\n<br />\n14:點解有D人用KANTE打前鋒 C朗打CM?<br />\n答: FIFA 19可以入場十字制直接轉陣 預先SET好戰術就可以夾好FULL CHEM入場再轉位<br />\n你鍾意C朗轉去打後衛都得<br />\n<br />\n15:抽到硬吹walkout又入唔到隊點算?<br />\n答:QUICK SELL囉屌你老母 抽撚完仲要PO圖扮慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n16:我DR SB 幾分幾分夠唔夠KEEP RANK 1?<br />\n答:<a href=\"https://www.futbin.com/division-rivals/division\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.futbin.com%2Fdivision-rivals%2Fdivision&d=CH2%2BOu%2FXd5cykt%2BSaDfKp0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=5ee46a6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.futbin.com/division-rivals/division</a><br />\n自己上網CHECK<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n派獎時間<br />\nSB：逢星期1朝早8點<br />\nDR：逢星期4晏晝3點<br />\nWL：逢星期4晏晝4點<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9008bb72bc96fa50f15f7597c8d27da1db9b0b3","tid":988300,"uid":121450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T03:00:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c2PDQPP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc2PDQPP.png&h=94f221f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36aa089e761beae253cb18cec0e458a0d6805239","tid":988300,"uid":188520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T03:12:41.000Z","msg":"上陣轉下陣算upgrade 嗎？<br />\n<br />\n入場轉4231, 拜山/Keane打LB，年長打中CAM/右CDM<br />\n<br />\n聖卡斯我知廢但有愛，當練移籠<br />\n<br />\n有tick係硬吹<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上陣:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EDC6fjh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEDC6fjh.png&h=0195fe3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下陣:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tqgSaSS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtqgSaSS.png&h=af47fde3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"292375ce01f37e54680ca95098aa9d4159643e12","tid":988300,"uid":24569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T03:14:40.000Z","msg":"點解會有兩個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31aba51ae32a0dd4423105353426294ebcb6de8f","tid":988300,"uid":158987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T06:03:29.000Z","msg":"我想問下點樣第一時間射門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多時都帶多一下 跟住就起唔到腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}